    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner. Whether you're heading to work or hitting the road for a trip, it\u2019s super reliable and runs beautifully. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it, so it's ready to go whenever you are. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates, and the suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally linear. A true driver\u2019s spec with a clean title and documented service history.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
