      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera delivers a visceral, analog experience powered by a 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile shifts, while the chassis maintains excellent kinematic integrity. Crucially, this example has been updated with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal, mitigating common M96 vulnerabilities. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the braking system\u2014utilizing four-piston monobloc calipers and vented rotors\u2014offers firm, fade-resistant modulation. A technically sound, well-sorted platform for the discerning enthusiast.",
